/**
 * Billing Seeder — initial feature catalogue and plan definitions.
 *
 * ─── This file is a BOOTSTRAP, not configuration ──────────────────────────────
 * It populates MongoDB with a sensible starting catalogue. Once seeded, the
 * database is authoritative: change prices, limits, descriptions or active
 * status by editing the documents (Atlas UI, Compass, or an admin endpoint).
 * Do NOT edit this file to change live pricing — re-running the seeder is
 * idempotent and will not overwrite operator changes (see `upsertPlan`).
 *
 * Run with:  npm run seed:billing
 */

